nse%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20timing%20felt%20urgent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20move%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20small%20three-bedroom%20duplex%20in%20Calgary%2C%20where%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Faverage-closing-costs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20mortgage%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%202%2C900%20Canadian%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20roughly%20%242%2C300%20USD%20at%20the%20time.%20Our%20daughter%2C%20then%203%2C%20was%20in%20full-time%20day%20care%20(another%20C%241%2C000-plus%20a%20month).%20Our%2011-month-old%20son%20was%20still%20in%20diapers%20and%20stayed%20at%20home%20with%20my%20wife%20before%20our%20move.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20relied%20heavily%20on%20takeout%20because%20we%20were%20too%20exhausted%20to%20cook%20or%20meal%20prep.%20With%20gas%2C%20car%20insurance%2C%20parking%20downtown%2C%20and%20all%20the%20%26quot%3Bconvenience%26quot%3B%20spending%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20short%20on%20time%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20treading%20water%20financially.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20started%20looking%20at%20Nelson%2C%20finding%20a%20home%20for%20our%20family%20in%20the%20idyllic%20mountain%20town%20felt%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20fantasy.%20Then%20we%20came%20across%20a%20modest%20three-bedroom%20heritage%20house%20for%20rent%20at%20C%241%2C600%20a%20month%2C%20much%20less%20than%20a%20similar%20place%20would've%20cost%20us%20in%20the%20city.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20renting%20for%20a%20couple%20years%2C%20we%20bought%20a%20house%20about%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20our%20monthly%20mortgage%20is%20now%20just%20under%20C%243%2C100.%20Groceries%20cost%20about%20the%20same%20in%20Nelson%2C%20but%20we%20stopped%20eating%20out%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-dinners-under-30-minutes-meal-planning-reci