h%20open%20arms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20began%20eating%20dinner%20together%20every%20night.%20No%20more%20laptops%20on%20the%20counter%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-reveals-why-email-most-powerful-productivity-tool-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echecking%20emails%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20working%20late%20nights%20at%20the%20office%2C%20missing%20bedtime%20with%20the%20kids.%20Afterward%2C%20we'd%20go%20for%20walks%20to%20the%20lake%20or%20hike%20in%20the%20abundance%20of%20trails%20in%20the%20woods%20skirting%20the%20town.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2968324-fb12-4312-aeb0-1b4d42cccff7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithout%20realizing%20it%2C%20we%20had%20traded%20urgency%20for%20presence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20our%20lifestyle%20overhaul%20wasn't%20painless%20or%20stress-free.%20There%20were%20plenty%20of%20tradeoffs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecided-raise-kids-family-near-grandparents-pros-and-cons-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosest%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20now%20live%20a%20seven-hour%20drive%20away.%20We%20can't%20call%20them%20for%20a%20quick%20babysitting%20favor%20or%20drop%20the%20kids%20off%20when%20one%20of%20us%20is%20sick.%20We%20miss%20them%20and%20our%20regular%20visits%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20most%20challenging%20part.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20job%20opportunities%20here%2C%20and%20though%20we%20spend%20less%2C%20it%20took%20about%20four%20years%20for%20us%20to%20start%20saving%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we've%20also%20gained%20so%20much.%20Our%20kids%20have%20more%20freedom%20and%20get%20to%20participate%20in%20self-directed%20play%20with%20neighborhood%20kids.%20They%20ride%20their%20bikes%20to