-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20Zealand's%20golden%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20the%20program%20launched%20its%20more%20lax%20requirements%20in%20April%2C%20it%20has%20received%20117%20applications%20from%20Americans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20main%20reason%3F%20Politics%2C%20says%20a%20concierge%20who%20helps%20the%20wealthy%20relocate%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20from%20around%20the%20world%20flocked%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20in%20search%20of%20gold.%20Two%20hundred%20years%20later%2C%20they%20are%20coming%20back%2C%20this%20time%20in%20search%20of%20golden%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealand-golden-visa-investor-rules-attract-wealthy-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20Zealand%20relaxed%20the%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20its%20golden%20visa%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0formally%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bactive%20investor%20plus%26quot%3B%20visa%20%E2%80%94%20which%20allows%20foreigners%20to%20gain%20permanent%20residency%20status%20by%20investing%20in%20the%20country's%20economy.%20It%20still%2C%20however%2C%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20cash%3A%20Applicants%20must%20invest%20at%20least%205%20million%20New%20Zealand%20dollars%2C%20about%20%243%20million%2C%20over%20three%20years%20or%20%2410%20million%20New%20Zealand%20dollars%20over%20five%20years%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20type%20of%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20surge%20of%20Americans%20has%20attempted%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20new%20rules.%20Since%20the%20April%201%20rule%20changes%2C%20New%20Zealand%20has%20received%20267%20golden%20visa%20applications%20as%20of%20August%208%2C%20compared%20to%20115%20between%20September%202022%20and%20March%2031%2C%202025%2C%20according%20to%20New%20Zealand's%20immigration%20site.%20Of%20the%20new%20applications%2C%2044%25%20are%20from%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3