e%20Foot%20Locker%20and%20Snipes%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20deepest%20markdowns%2C%C2%A0while%20Nike's%20stores%20have%20a%20broader%20selection.%C2%A0That's%20based%20on%20my%C2%A0store%20checks%20in%20New%20York%2C%20including%20Nike's%20new%20location%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20two%20Foot%20Locker%20stores%2C%20streetwear%20retailer%20Snipes%2C%20and%20Urban%20Outfitters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike%20is%20facing%20heightened%20competition%20this%20back-to-school%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20footwear%20survey%20by%20investment%20bank%20Stifel%20of%20over%20100%20stores%20found%20that%20Nike's%20popularity%20lost%20ground%20this%20back-to-school%20season%2C%20though%20it%20was%20still%20the%20most%20popular%20brand%20in%20stores.%20The%20stores%20referenced%20Nike%20as%20one%20of%20their%20most%20popular%20brands%20in%2087%25%20of%20the%20firm's%20checks%2C%20down%20from%2097%25%20during%20the%20back-to-school%20season%20four%20years%20ago.%20Competitors%20like%20New%20Balance%20and%20Adidas%20gained%20popularity%2C%20as%20Nike's%20retro%20styles%20like%20Dunks%2C%20Air%20Force%201%2C%20and%20Jordan%201%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike%20is%20also%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20CEO%20Elliott%20Hill%20told%20Fortune%20that%20Nike%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Btoo%20promotional.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20company%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-cutting-discounts-in-2025-ceo-says-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecut%20back%20on%20markdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20provide%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Belevated%26quot%3B%20experience%20beginning%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20company%20said%20that%20it%20was%20planning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-raising-prices-us-expects-1-billion-tariff-hit-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bsurgical%26quot%3B%20price%20hikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20would%20