3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20visited%202%20Foot%20Locker%20locations%20around%20New%20York%20City.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222645%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foot%20Locker%20storefront%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b05d24194a2d49b8af5734%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20a%20Brooklyn%20Foot%20Locker%20and%20another%20in%20the%20SoHo%20neighborhood%20in%20the%20last%20weeks%20of%20August.%20From%20all%20of%20my%20store%20checks%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20Foot%20Locker%20had%20the%20best%20deals%20for%20back-to-school%20shoppers.%20A%20pair%20of%20black%20and%20white%20Nike%20Dunks%2C%20for%20example%2C%20was%20marked%20down%20to%20%2475.%20At%20the%20Nike%20store%2C%20they%20were%20%24115.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Nike%20wasn't%20the%20star%20of%20the%20show%20at%20the%20Brooklyn%20Foot%20Locker%20location.%20When%20I%20walked%20in%2C%20I%20was%20met%20with%20a%20prominent%20Adidas%20display%20at%20the%20front%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20from%20Stifel%2C%20Adidas%20is%20hitting%20its%20peak%20in%20popularity%20with%20styles%20like%20the%20retro%20Samba%20driving%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20dropped%20by%20Snipes%20on%20my%20way%20home%20to%20see%20what%20sort%20of%20deals%20it%20has.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snipes%20storefront%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b05cf0a17a8c5b4053a519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESnipes%20was%20packed%20on%20a%20Wednesday%20evening%20with%20families%20trying%20on%20different%20shoes.%20Similar%20to%20Foot%20Locker%2C%20many%20of%20the%20display%20shoes%20had%20bright%20red%20tags%20indicating%20