g%20remorse%20for%20the%20victims%20she%20financially%20defrauded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20around%20and%20doing%20%26quot%3Bthe%20bare%20minimum%26quot%3B%20will%20make%20%26quot%3Bevery%20day%20feel%20like%20Groundhog%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%20Paperny%20said.%20FPC%20Bryan%2C%20he%20said%2C%20offers%20opportunities%20to%20work%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20more%20easily%20correspond%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Ghislaine%20can%20do%20that%2C%20they%20set%20themselves%20up%20for%20more%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20people%20don't%20do%20that%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20the%20prison%20term%20feels%20like%20an%20eternity%20because%20you%20just%20sit%20around%20playing%20the%20blame%20game%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20absolutely%20miserable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FPC%20Bryan%20in%20Texas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b0c030a17a8c5b4053b3a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20federal%20prison%20camp%20in%20Bryan%2C%20Texas%2C%20where%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20has%20been%20transferred.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%20between%20a%20camp%20like%20FPC%20Bryan%20and%20other%20prisons%20is%20that%20it%20provides%20work%20opportunities.%20According%20to%20the%202023%20handbook%2C%20FPC%20Bryan%20requires%20all%20inmates%20to%20hold%20a%20job%20assignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20how%20appealing%20the%20positions%20will%20be%20for%20Maxwell%2C%20an%20Oxford%20University%20graduate.%20The%20handbook%20says%20opportunities%20are%20available%20through%20the%20company%20UNICOR%2C%20which%20produces%20services%20and%20operates%20factories%20that%20make%20products%20for%20the%20federal%20government.%20Examples%20of%20UNICOR%20products%20and%20services%20listed%20in%20the%20handbook%20include%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Belectronic%20cable%20assemblies%2C%20executive%20and%20systems%20furniture%2C%20metal%20pallet%20racks%2C%20stainless%20steel%20food%20service%20equipment%2C%20mattresses%2C%20towels%2C%20utility%20bags%2C%20brooms%2C%20data%20entry%2C%20signage%2C%20and%20printing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20may%20also%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20teach%20yoga%2C%20pilates%2C%20and%20other%20physical%20fitness%20classes.%20The%20handbook%20says%20FPC%20Bryan%20also%20offers%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20though%20Maxwell%20would%20be%20required%20to%20ship%20her%20projects%20out%20of%20the%20facility%20after%20they%20are%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20facility's%20commissary%20list%20offers%20some%20intriguing%20food%20options.%20Maxwell%20could%20buy%20Thai%20noodles%2C%20caramel%20candies%2C%20Nutella%2C%20salmon%2C%20shredded%20beef%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commissary%20list%20also%20includes%20a%20large%20selection%20of%20shampoos%20and%20cosmetics%2C%20like%20lip%20gloss%20and%20hair%20dye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Maxwell%20were%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20standard%20BOP%20%26quot%3BNational%20Menu%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20includes%20a%20%26quot%3Bno%20flesh%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Paperny%20said%20she%20would%20be%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20worked%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20Paperny%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20see%20meat%20that%20had%20expiration%20dates%20that%20had%20passed.%20I%20mean%2C%20veggies%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20look%20like%20vegetables.%20They%20look%20like%20they've%20been%20in%20the%20sun%20for%202%2C000%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-federal-prison-camp-transfer-bryan-texas-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756719061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b1dfb7a1