%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20But%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20grafted%20plant%20from%20the%20nursery%20and%20plant%20it%2C%20you%20will%20start%20getting%20fruits%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhijeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20gently%20place%20the%20sapling%20in%20the%20prepared%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20roots%20are%20spread%20out.%20Water%20thoroughly%20to%20settle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20time%20for%20planting%20is%20June%20to%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Regular%20care%20and%20monitoring%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20the%20plant%20whenever%20the%20topsoil%20is%20dry.%20Check%20soil%20moisture%20and%20set%20up%20watering%20schedules.%20You%20can%20use%20organic%20pesticides%20like%20neem%20oil%20to%20protect%20from%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Harvest%20your%20jackfruits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%20Jackfruit%20trees%20typically%20take%20three%20to%20five%20years%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20following%20these%20tips%2C%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20rewarding%20experience%20of%20growing%20your%20jackfruit%20tree%2C%20reaping%20its%20delicious%20and%20nutritious%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20now%2C%20and%20let%20the%20journey%20of%20nurturing%20begin!%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756557000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D493680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20monsoon%2C%20Immerse%20in%20season%E2%80%99s%20delights%20with%20homegrown%20jackfruit.%20From%20sunlight%20to%20sapling%20care%2C%20cultivate%20this%20superfood%20using%20tips%20from%20gardeners%20Abhijeet%20Prajapati%20and%20Mini%20Sreekumar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493680%2Fhow-to-grow-jackfruit-tree-at-home-simple-ultimate-gardening-guide%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20You%20Know%20This%20Kannada%20Actress%20Who%20Has%20Rescued%204000%2B%20Animals%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%E2%80%99s%20through%20her%20work%20or%20passion%2C%20Samyukta%20Hornad%20ensures%20she%E2%80%99s%20changing%20animals%E2%80%99%20lives.%20The%20actress%E2%80%99s%20work%20spans%20roles%20in%20the%20Kannada%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20she%20is%20loved%20even%20beyond%20the%20silver%20screen.%20Samyukta%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20animals%20began%20one%20day%20when%20she%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20puppy%20stuck%20in%20a%20drain.%20She%20adopted%20him%20and%20named%20him%20Gunda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samyukta%20Hornad%20rescues%20animals%20and%20sees%20to%20their%20rehabilitation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fanimal-welfare-1756203932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-492059%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESamyukta%20Hornad%20rescues%20animals%20and%20sees%20to%20their%20rehabilitation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Gunda%E2%80%99s%20passing%20that%20firmed%20Samyukta%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20in%20animal%20care.%20She%20founded%20%E2%80%98The%20Praana%20Foundation%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20NGO%20that%20looks%20after%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353705%2Fmumbai-police-officer-saving-animals-from-abuse-sudhir-kudalkar-stray-dogs-cases-pure-animal-lovers-group%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rehabilitation%20and%20rescue%20of%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20cats.%20The%20foundation%20has%20a%20cat%20rehabilitation%20and%20adoption%20centre%20that%20rescues%20and%20rehabilitates%20stray%20and%20abandoned%20cats%20and%20helps%20them%20find%20loving%20homes.%20It%20was%20recently%20awarded%20%E2%80%98Best%20Animal%20Rights%20NGO%E2%80%99%20at%20the%207th%20CMSB%20National%20Award%20(2025).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20Samyukta%20has%20helped%20rescue%204%2C000%20animals%20and%20has%20also%20been%20instrumental%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20free%20ambulance%20to%20rescue%20and%20treat%20injured%20strays.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A491751%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3