20Instead%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F492080%2Frang-de-peer-to-peer-lending-model-of-loans-helps-farmers-purchase-decentralised-renewable-energy-solutions-like-solar-dryers-hydroponics-units%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDRE%20technologies%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20Indian%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20of%20impacting%20three%20crore%20livelihoods.%20And%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20helping%20script%20this%20success%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPowering%20rural%20futures%20with%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20steadily%20being%20propelled%20towards%20a%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%20This%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20plummeting%20costs%20of%20solar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dramatic%2095%20percent%20drop%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20photovoltaic%20modules%20from%20over%20Rs%20200%20per%20watt%20in%202010%20to%20under%20Rs%209%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20empowering%20people%20in%20rural%20India%20through%20solar%20powered%20atta%20chakkis%20that%20help%20them%20turn%20to%20entrepreneurship%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-493600%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20empowering%20people%20in%20rural%20India%20through%20solar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20help%20them%20turn%20to%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Jain%2C%20Fellow%20and%20Director%2C%20Green%20Economy%20and%20Impact%20Innovations%2C%20CEEW%2C%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20this%20plunge%20in%20prices%20is%20making%20green%20applications%20affordable.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20started%20realising%20that%20solar%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20so%20many%20other%20productive%20applications%20beyond%20consumptive%20use%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20missing%20gap%20was%20how%20to%20make%20these%20appliances%20efficient%3B%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20trying%20to%20solve%20for%20this%20by%20creating%20energy-efficient%20appliances.%E2%80%9D%20These%20appliances%20are%20now%20creating%20quite%20a%20stir%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20they%20are%20being%20introduced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plausible%20reason%20could%20be%20the%20increased%20earnings%20following%20DRE%20tech%20adoption.%20As%20pointed%20out%20by%20a%20CEEW%20report%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20those%20who%20adopted%20a%20DRE%20solution%20reported%20income%20growth%2C%20typically%20achieving%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20INR%2040%2C000%20(with%20an%20average%20usage%20of%20eight%20months)%2C%20a%2033%20percent%20increase%20compared%20to%20their%20baseline%20earnings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20earnings%20are%20one%20side%20of%20the%20story%2C%20the%20other%20side%20is%20expenditure.%20Naveen%20admits%20he%E2%80%99d%20never%20have%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20it%20weren%E2%80%99t%20for%20a%20subsidy%20scheme.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20cost%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20Almost%2050%20percent%20of%20this%20cost%20was%20borne%20by%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%2C%20and%20I%20only%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%205%2C20%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20am%20paying%20back%20through%20an%20EMI%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20economics%20of%20going%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomic%20relief%20is%20key%2C%20Naveen%20explains.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20what%20got%20him%20to%20say%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%20to%20entrepreneurship.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20studying%20for%20a%20government%20job.%20But%20I%20began%20seeing%20how%20so%20many%20people%20in%20my%20hometown%20of%20Sitapur%20were%20starting%20to%20purchase%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Datta%2Bchakki%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Datta%2Bchakki%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyCQgAEEUYORigATIGCAEQRRg9MgYIAhBFGD3SAQgzOTM0ajBqN6gCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20These%20micro-preneurs%20did%20not%20have%20to%20brave%20the%20throes%20of%20fluctuating%20electricity%20dynamics%20anymore.%20Their%20output%20was%20instead%20guided%20by%20the%20rhythms%20of%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20revealed%20to%20Naveen%2C%20they%20felt%20more%20confident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20puts%20into%20perspective%20how%20Tushar%20Devidayal%2C%20CEO%20at%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%2C%20views%20green%20energy.%20He%20underscores%20how%20adopting%20clean%20tech%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20alternative%20anymore%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20starting%20to%20become%20the%20most%20viable%20solution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1-1756464762.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20every%20step%20in%20the%20process%2C%20the%20associates%20part%20of%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions'%20network%20work%20with%20the%20people%20in%20the%20villages%20to%20implement%20the%20technology%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1-1756464762.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1-1756464762-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1-1756464762-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1-1756464762-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1-1756464762-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-493602%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDD%20Solar%E2%80%99s%20business%20associates%20help%20villagers%20adopt%20and%20run%20the%20technology%20at%20every%20step.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20the%20solar%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20sugarcane%20crushers%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20clear%20need%20for%20them.%20Running%20on%20diesel%20is%20incredibly%20expensive.%20Even%20if%20you%20park%20the%20climate%20part%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%2C%20the%20NOX%20emissions%20(harmful%20nitrogen%20oxides%20from%20fuel%20combustion)%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20is%20someone%20grinding%20flour%20at%20Rs%2025%20a%20unit.%20Then%20again%2C%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20stable%20three-phase%20power%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20they%20go%20to%20a%20mini%20grid%20operator%2C%20where%20the%20cost%20is%20prohibitive%2C%20around%20Rs%2025%20a%20unit.%20It%20eats%20into%20their%20margins.%20So%2C%20solar%20just%20makes%20sense.%20At%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366571%2Fkalpana-sankar-hand-in-hand-india-access-to-financial-inclusion-tamil-nadu-percy-barnevik%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowering%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20empowering%20people%20to%20make%20their%20own%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20clean%20tech%20affordable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20convince%20someone%20about%20the%20power%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20take%20them%20to%20watch%20a%20real-life%20success%20story.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20any%20capital%20expense%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20convince%20a%20rural%20customer.%20Only%20when%20they%20see%20the%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20or%20when%20you%20compare%20the%20profits%20to%20the%20operating%20expenses%20will%20they%20see%20reason%20to%20adopt%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20adds.%20Purchasing%20a%20product%20that%20costs%20upwards%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20(a%20typical%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E)%20is%20not%20something%20most%20of%20them%20can%20afford%2C%20he%20reasons%2C%20pointing%20to%20how%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20working%20with%20NBFCs%20to%20unlock%20loans%20for%20these%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20earnings%20are%20about%20three%20times%20the%20monthly%20EMI.%20If%20you%20consider%20an%20oil%20expeller%20(a%20device%20that%20extracts%20oil%20from%20seeds)%2C%20the%20person%20will%20be%20making%20around%20Rs%2060%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20with%20an%20EMI%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20higher%20than%20Rs%2025%2C000%20a%20month.%E2%